[normal]Early indications are that t
[normal]he use of 
[normal]Demand Responsive Transport [
[normal]DRT
[normal]]
[normal] facilities to link with conventional services, effectively linking small settlements to the ‘Normal Routes’ which serve the bigger villages 
[normal]in the same area
[normal], could be a positive step
[normal] – i.e. judgements on Routes 
[normal]rather than location
